headline: Altria (MO): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: Altria has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 9.5%. The stock now trades at $59.65, marking a 14.5% gain. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
